  ┬╖ exact subset_span тЯиk, (update_of_ne hjk.symm ..).symmтЯй
  ┬╖ nth_rw 2 [тЖР add_sub_cancel_right (v j) (r тАв v i)]
    exact sub_mem (subset_span тЯиj, update_self ..тЯй)
      (smul_mem _ _ (subset_span тЯиi, update_of_ne hij ..тЯй))
  ┬╖ exact subset_span тЯиk, update_of_ne hjk.symm ..тЯй

